<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover, maximum-scale=1" />
<title>台股技術分析報表產生器</title>
<meta name="description" content="從 Google Sheet 讀取股票代號，自動抓取股價、計算技術指標並產生投資建議 Excel 報表" />

<!-- PWA -->
<link rel="manifest" href="./manifest.json" />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#1f497d" />
<link rel="icon" href="./icons/favicon-32.png" sizes="32x32" type="image/png" />
<link rel="icon" href="./icons/favicon-16.png" sizes="16x16" type="image/png" />
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="./icons/apple-touch-icon.png" />

<!-- iOS 安裝支援 -->
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent" />
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="台股報表" />

<link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css" />
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">

  <!-- ── Top App Bar ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div id="topbar">
    <div class="brand">
      <img src="./icons/icon-96.png" alt="" />
      <span class="title">台股技術分析報表產生器</span>
    </div>
    <span id="status-dot" title="連線狀態"></span>
    <button class="icon-btn" id="reload-btn" title="重新整理" aria-label="重新整理">⟳</button>
    <button class="icon-btn" id="settings-btn" title="設定後端網址" aria-label="設定">⚙</button>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Main content: embeds the existing Gradio app.py UI ── -->
  <div id="main">
    <iframe
      id="app-frame"
      title="台股技術分析報表產生器"
      allow="clipboard-write"
    ></iframe>

    <!-- Settings overlay -->
    <div id="settings-screen" class="screen">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>🔧 連接後端服務</h2>
        <p class="hint">
          本 App 是既有 Python / Gradio 分析工具（<code>app.py</code>）的
          PWA 外殼。請先在伺服器或本機執行：<br />
          <code>python app.py</code><br />
          再輸入該服務的網址（例如 <code>http://localhost:7860</code>
          或您部署到雲端後的網域）。
        </p>

        <label for="backend-url-input">後端服務網址</label>
        <input
          id="backend-url-input"
          type="url"
          inputmode="url"
          autocomplete="off"
          autocapitalize="off"
          spellcheck="false"
          placeholder="http://localhost:7860"
        />

        <div class="presets" id="presets-wrap"></div>

        <div class="row-btns">
          <button class="ghost" id="cancel-settings-btn">取消</button>
          <button class="primary" id="connect-btn">連線</button>
        </div>

        <div class="badge">🔒 網址僅儲存在本機裝置（localStorage）</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Loading overlay -->
    <div id="loading-screen" class="screen hidden">
      <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div class="spinner"></div>
        <h2>連線中…</h2>
        <p class="hint">正在連接分析服務，請稍候</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Offline / connect-failed overlay -->
    <div id="offline-screen" class="screen hidden">
      <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
        <h2>⚠️ 無法連接服務</h2>
        <p class="hint">
          目前無法連上後端服務，請確認：<br />
          1. <code>app.py</code> 是否已啟動<br />
          2. 網址是否正確、裝置是否連上同一網路<br />
          3. 網路連線是否正常
        </p>
        <div class="row-btns">
          <button class="ghost" id="open-settings-from-offline">變更網址</button>
          <button class="primary" id="retry-offline-btn">重試</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Install toast ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <div id="install-toast" class="hidden">
    <img src="./icons/icon-96.png" alt="" width="40" height="40" style="border-radius:10px;" />
    <div class="txt">
      <b>安裝到主畫面</b>
      像原生 App 一樣快速啟動，並支援離線提示畫面
    </div>
    <button class="ghost" id="dismiss-install-btn">稍後</button>
    <button class="primary" id="install-btn" style="flex:none;padding:10px 14px;">安裝</button>
  </div>

</div>

<script src="./app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
